{
  "stem": "22174.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And in Germany, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] all kids go first public school and until the age of 10.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then the people, the children of families who could afford the tuition for the high school, which was oriented towards university studies.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And it was part of the educational-- of the national educational [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] system.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But they charged tuition.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "In Germany, people-- especially the working class-- they couldn't afford it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So at 10, I started what was called the Gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was the name of that-- of those high schools.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And there I went through the age of 18.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was the highest grade.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The grades were called Latin names, you know, because [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] of the school and the atmosphere of this [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So the highest-- the lowest grade was Sexta.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This means six.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the highest grade was the Prima, Uberprima, Upper Prima.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was the highest grade.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then we had to pass [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] examination, which would give us what we needed to enter university.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] just four weeks before the examination, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was forced to leave the school, so I couldn't take the examination.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that's a long story.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Can I drink?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[DRINKS] I was very good in art, especially in drawing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I made-- at that time the political situation was very [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] hectic and violent.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And traditionally, the Jews were-- either left-wing-- left-wing",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "communists, socialists, social democrats, democrats.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father was a social democrat, card-carrying social democrat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so I was even further to the left at that time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was already 18-- 17, 18 years old.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I made cartoons, political cartoons.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
